1. *Večere* ćemo u restoranu. (We will have dinner at the restaurant.)
2. Ona se *večeras* odlučila da počne dijetu. (She has decided to start a diet tonight.)
3. On je naredio *večeru* u hotelu. (He ordered dinner at the hotel.)
4. Očekujemo da će *večerati* sa nama. (We expect that they will have dinner with us.)
5. *Večerio* sam sa svojim prijateljima. (I had dinner with my friends.)